         <t:abstract>
            <t:p><t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3082Chaine">Marius Chaîne</t:persName> mistakenly identified this malkǝʾ-hymn as the one for
               <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9848Walatta">Walatta Ṗeṭros</t:persName> in 
               <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/69U7EH56"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Chaine1913RepPart1"/><title level="a">Répertoire des Salam et Malkeʾe contenus dans les manuscrits éthiopiens des bibliothèques d’Europe</title><title level="j">Revue de l’Orient Chrétien</title><author><forename>Marius</forename><surname>Chaîne</surname></author><date>1913</date><biblScope unit="volume">18</biblScope><biblScope unit="issue">2 (Deuxième série, 8/2)</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">183–203</biblScope><note type="url">http://catholicapedia.net/Documents/Revue-de-l.Orient-chretien/18-1913_revue-de-l.orient-ch_paris.pdf</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Chaine1913RepPart1</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Chaine1913RepPart1</note><t:citedRange unit="page">202</t:citedRange></t:bibl>, but correctly indentified this as a malkǝʾ-hymn to 
               <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3698ehetaKr">ʾƎḫǝta Krǝstos</t:persName> in 
               <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/GADX9HRE"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Chaine1912Catalogue"/><title level="m">Catalogue des manuscrits éthiopiens de la Collection Antoine d’Abbadie</title><author><forename>Marius</forename><surname>Chaîne</surname></author><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><publisher>Imprimerie nationale–Ernest Leroux, éditeur</publisher><date>1912</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/cataloguedesmanu00bibluoft</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">Bibliothèque Nationale</note><note type="tag">bm:Chaine1912Catalogue</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">Bibliothèque Nationale</note><note type="tag">bm:Chaine1912Catalogue</note><t:citedRange unit="page">57</t:citedRange><t:citedRange unit="number">88</t:citedRange></t:bibl>. The malkǝʾ is usually followed by <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3072RepCh352">Hymn to Walatta
                                                  Ṗeṭros</t:ref>
             </t:p>
         </t:abstract>
